            "type": "Video Article",
            "title": "7 - 9 Muaj: I kalon objektet nga njëra dorë në tjetrën pa vështirësi, i tund ato",
            "created_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2022-02-09T16:01:41+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003EWed, 02/09/2022 - 16:01\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "updated_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-02-10T05:02:09+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003ETue, 02/10/2026 - 05:02\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "summary": "",
